This paper discusses the modeling of robotics applications, which falls under the category of Cyber-Physical Systems (CPS). The paper specifically focuses on the integration of six different modeling languages to model the logical software architecture and system behavior of CPS. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SE (Software Engineering), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.PL (Programming Languages), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science).
